track_notes: Plenty room to park, the forest is very nice in autumn, the walk is short and easy. Need to look at the track, because there are lot of path.
I upload this track, not much different as the first one, just because the forest road are larger and better. Plenty room on summit for antenna. we went here in summertime; it is very very hot.

Starting from this side, on the forest road is ok if you can drive a 4x4. Otherwise you must walk 2 km more..but you can use a bicycle and this is ok.
The last part of the walk is a bit slope. Plenty room for antenna on summit. More info at f6hbi
